<view class="app-page staff-page"><view class="app-card app-card--glass staff-head"><view class="flex-row items-center justify-between"><view class="flex-row items-center"><view class="staff-avatar"><text class="staff-avatar-text">{{a}}</text></view><view class="flex-col ml-12"><text class="staff-name">{{b}}</text><text class="staff-subline">{{c}} · {{d}}</text></view></view><view class="staff-chip"><text class="staff-chip-dot"></text><text class="staff-chip-text">信息可编辑</text></view></view><view class="staff-tip"><text class="staff-tip-text">建议完善联系方式与科室信息，便于任务派发与跨科室协作。</text></view></view><view class="app-card staff-form"><text class="app-section-title">我的信息管理</text><view class="kv"><text class="k">姓名</text><input class="v-input" placeholder="请输入姓名" value="{{e}}" bindinput="{{f}}"/></view><view class="kv"><text class="k">工号</text><input class="v-input" placeholder="例如：A1023" value="{{g}}" bindinput="{{h}}"/></view><view class="kv"><text class="k">科室</text><input class="v-input" placeholder="例如：心内科" value="{{i}}" bindinput="{{j}}"/></view><view class="kv"><text class="k">岗位</text><input class="v-input" placeholder="例如：随访护士/责任医生" value="{{k}}" bindinput="{{l}}"/></view><view class="kv"><text class="k">手机号</text><input class="v-input" placeholder="用于随访联络" value="{{m}}" bindinput="{{n}}"/></view><view class="kv"><text class="k">负责片区</text><input class="v-input" placeholder="例如：新城区·北片区" value="{{o}}" bindinput="{{p}}"/></view><view class="staff-actions"><view class="btn-secondary staff-btn" bindtap="{{q}}">重置</view><view class="btn-secondary staff-btn" bindtap="{{r}}">保存</view></view><text class="staff-save-hint">{{s}}</text></view><view class="app-card staff-settings"><text class="app-section-title">设置与支持</text><view class="row" bindtap="{{t}}"><view class="flex-row items-center"><text class="row-ico">🧹</text><text class="row-text">清除本地缓存</text></view><text class="row-arrow">›</text></view><view class="line"></view><view class="row" bindtap="{{v}}"><view class="flex-row items-center"><text class="row-ico">☎️</text><text class="row-text">联系管理员/技术支持</text></view><text class="row-arrow">›</text></view></view><view class="app-card staff-logout"><view class="btn-danger" bindtap="{{w}}">退出登录</view></view><staff-tabbar wx:if="{{x}}" u-i="9bd69124-0" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{x}}"></staff-tabbar></view>